---
title: Balsamic Rosemary Chicken with Pesto Garlic Toast & Broccoli
description: We believe pork chops are a canvas. Tonight’s palette for your palate: A saucy coating that includes fresh rosemary, tangy balsamic vinegar, and creamy garlic herb butter—because why choose one when you could have them all? Complement those chops with a side of pesto-garlic-herb toast and roasted broccoli, and you have yourself a dinner to Remem-brandt.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6492eb393477e872b82f0227-a6ce5ff4.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64932c054b18c31a619ff719.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 20m
